text: Colobothea pleuralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Casey in 1913. It is known from Costa Rica and Panama.BioLib.cz - Colobothea pleuralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1913
title: Colobothea pleuralis
